{"tid":1790742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[l被代表] 楊千嬅獲習近平握手　代表香港為文藝晚會獻唱","createTime":"2019-12-20T08:25:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T08:29:01.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"14a2b7cc173acabecaf1126185ce38883ab02e2d","tid":1790742,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3733293/org/e071ce5a92269339752505c67016f33c.jpeg/9jnuB1ZnEsfp3iG985At7tYXBO7hVHDrp9iSJafYkiU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3733293%2Forg%2Fe071ce5a92269339752505c67016f33c.jpeg%2F9jnuB1ZnEsfp3iG985At7tYXBO7hVHDrp9iSJafYkiU&h=1b09be4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n澳門回歸20年昨晚舉行文藝晚會，今年的主題是濠江情中國心，晚會歷時一個多小時，除了舞蹈及戲曲表演，亦有歌手獻唱，去到晚會尾聲，大會安排了中國、香港、台灣、澳門及澳門聾人協會一同表演獻唱《蓮成一家》，而楊千嬅是當中唯一代表香港的歌手，而唱畢後楊千嬅同一眾表演單位謝幕，更獲國家主席習近平握手致謝。其實十年前澳門亦舉行過慶祝回歸文藝晚會，當時亦有中港澳台歌手表演環節，譚晶、張學友、費玉清及何超儀獻唱《明天會更好》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3733292/org/65549dab3424bc75838097550dc9f0fc.jpeg/iKaBjxL2RLet-fk3OBefXrOpXtWXwR8VbFKWaGxSlmg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3733292%2Forg%2F65549dab3424bc75838097550dc9f0fc.jpeg%2FiKaBjxL2RLet-fk3OBefXrOpXtWXwR8VbFKWaGxSlmg&h=6e7ae4db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3733300/org/604a385e5c98340a24e5254ac43018f7.jpeg/cTan2exhLkPdUE-5ydu8VM7ZasY070OuIDqw-SA6sPk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3733300%2Forg%2F604a385e5c98340a24e5254ac43018f7.jpeg%2FcTan2exhLkPdUE-5ydu8VM7ZasY070OuIDqw-SA6sPk&h=fda417b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87786112d550d5a14872cec62d3fc7871c6f8a1a","tid":1790742,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:26:59.000Z","msg":"人瑞個身有冇暖返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a58628432580173716925f